sual-analysis worker before measurement\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"It couples independent features and release boundaries without proven compute residency.\\\"}],\\\"graphEvents\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"q-visual-analysis-practicality\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"QUESTION\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Practical visual analysis features\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-dom-layout-plane\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"DOM already supplies layout geometry\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-screenshot-contract-gap\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Screenshot artifact contract is missing\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-phash-dedupe-only\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Perceptual hash serves dedupe and drift\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-multimodal-new-abi\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Multimodal retrieval needs a new ABI\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"c-rust-vision-conditional\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"CLAIM\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Rust is conditional for model execution only\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-crawler-visual-plane\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Design crawler screenshots and element styles\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-styles-schema-artifacts\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Styles schema and artifact allowlist\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-image-tooling-docs\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Sharp and image_hasher documentation\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-text-embed-contract\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Current text embedding contract\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-layout-answers-visual\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"f-dom-layout-plane\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"q-visual-analysis-practicality\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"ANSWERS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-contract-answers-visual\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"f-screenshot-contract-gap\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"q-visual-analysis-practicality\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"ANSWERS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-phash-answers-visual\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"f-phash-dedupe-only\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"q-visual-analysis-practicality\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"ANSWERS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-multimodal-answers-visual\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"f-multimodal-new-abi\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"q-visual-analysis-practicality\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"ANSWERS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-crawler-supports-layout\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"s-crawler-visual-plane\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"f-dom-layout-plane\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"SUPPORTS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-schema-supports-gap\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"s-styles-schema-artifacts\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"f-screenshot-contract-gap\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"SUPPORTS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-tools-support-phash\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"s-image-tooling-docs\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"f-phash-dedupe-only\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"SUPPORTS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-text-contract-supports-abi\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"s-text-embed-contract\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"f-multimodal-new-abi\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"SUPPORTS\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-abi-supports-conditional-rust\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"f-multimodal-new-abi\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"c-rust-vision-conditional\\\",\\\"relation\\\":\\\"SUPPORTS\\\"}],\\\"executor\\\":{\\\"kind\\\":\\\"cli-opencode\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\\\",\\\"reasoningEffort\\\":null,\\\"serviceTier\\\":null}}\\n \\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration_start\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":7,\\\"executor\\\":{\\\"kind\\\":\\\"cli-opencode\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\\\",\\\"reasoningEffort\\\":null,\\\"serviceTier\\\":null},\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T04:59:21.490Z\\\"}\\n+{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":7,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.74,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"This iteration separated offline/privacy value from implementation language, established the installed ONNX stack as the mandatory local multimodal oracle, distinguished ort from Candle by parity and packaging risk, and converted Rust adoption into worker-isolation and artifact-contract gates at 10x/100x scale.\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Assess on-device local text and image embedding models through Rust runtimes such as ONNX Runtime or Candle: capability, model residency, packaging, privacy/offline value, JS/native-addon alternatives, and current/10x/100x gates.\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":5,\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does local text/image inference require Rust?\\\",\\\"Which Rust runtime is the default candidate?\\\",\\\"Should a resident model use an addon or sidecar?\\\",\\\"What clears the current, 10x, and 100x runtime gates?\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[{\\\"approach\\\":\\\"Rust as privacy or offline enabler\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Locality follows model provisioning and network policy, not host language.\\\"},{\\\"approach\\\":\\\"Rust ort rewrite for inference speed\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Node and Rust wrappers execute the same native ONNX Runtime kernels.\\\"},{\\\"approach\\\":\\\"In-process native addon as default model host\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"It adds no kernel residency and loses sidecar crash and RSS isolation.\\\"},{\\\"approach\\\":\\\"Bundle model weights in npm or native binary\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Weights are large, licensed, profile-specific artifacts with an independent lifecycle.\\\"},{\\\"approach\\\":\\\"Candle as universal runtime\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Each model architecture, preprocessing path, backend, and numerical contract requires separate qualification.\\\"}],\\\"graphEvents\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"q-local-model-rust-gate\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"QUESTION\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Rust gate for local text and image models\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-ts-ort-local-baseline\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Existing Node stack supports offline multimodal inference\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-locality-runtime-neutral\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Privacy and offline value are runtime-neutral\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-ort-same-native-kernels\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Rust ort and Node share native kernels\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-candle-model-specific\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Candle value is model-specific\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f-model-store-contract\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"FINDING\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Models need an opt-in verified store\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"c-scale-gated-rust-worker\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"CLAIM\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Rust worker is conditional at 10x and 100x\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-repo-transformers-stack\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Repository Transformers.js stack\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-transformers-local-models\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Transformers.js local model controls\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-ort-node-platforms\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"ONNX Runtime Node platform matrix\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"node\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"s-candle-capabilities\\\",\\\"kind\\\":\\\"SOURCE\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"Candle models and backends\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"edge\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"e-baseline-answers-local-gate\\\",\\\"source\\\":\\\"f-ts-ort-local-baseline\\\",\\\"target\\\":\